title: Moving off the Cowboys; Teams at a Crossroads; NFC East Report Cards; Roger McCreary
itunes:title: Moving off the Cowboys; Teams at a Crossroads; NFC East Report Cards; Roger McCreary
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and 2x Super Bowl Champion LeSean McCoy examine which teams in the NFL need to make key offseason acquisitions and then take the next step towards success next season. Also, Kyle explains why he's done with the Dallas Cowboys; the crew hands out their report cards for the NFC East and they're joined by Roger McCreary and he talks about his combine workout, his standout moments in college football and his unique pregame meal.
